Class ShowList

java.lang.Object
ShowList
public class ShowList extends Object
A class that implements the ADT list by using a chain of nodes.

    • find

      public ShowList.ShowNode find (String showID)
      Returns the TV Show for a given ID. This method can leak private information since it is returning a reference to an object
      Parameters:
      showID - the ID of the TV Show to be returned
      Returns:
      the node in the list containing the TV Show with the given ID, or null if no such node exists One way to avoid this leakage is to make the ShowNode class private and/or make methods that extend the (private) find method such that the method can only be used by other ShowList methods
